properties.title: representative
properties.name: Glenn Thompson
properties.biography: Glenn Thompson, a Representative from Pennsylvania; born in Bellefonte, Centre County, Pa., July 27, 1959; B.S., Pennsylvania State University, University Park, Pa., 1981; M.Ed., Temple University, Philadelphia, Pa., 1988; rehabilitation therapist manager; member of the Bald Eagle, Pa., school board, 1990-1995; unsuccessful candidate for nomination to the Pennsylvania state house of representatives in 1998 and 2000; chairman, Centre County Pa., Republican Party, 2002-2008; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Eleventh and to the four succeeding Congresses (January 3, 2009-present).
